## Playwright Notes

- Use `chromium` browser
- `wait_for_load_state('networkidle')` after each search before extraction
- Scroll detection: stop when ads_count_after_scroll == ads_count_before_scroll
- Store Meta's internal ad identifier from `data-ad-id` attribute or equivalent DOM location
